fields.title: The Three Little Pigs
fields.author: Brenda Parks
fields.notes: Write the following events on the board: Three little pigs decided to leave their home; The first pig chose to build his home out of straw; He built his house and sat down to eat his lunch of pea soup, salad, and bread; A hungry wolf knocked on his door; He demanded to be let in, but the pig refused; The wolf inhaled deeply; He blew the house down; All that remained was a haystack; The little pig went to his brother's house. Discuss and circle the events that are the most important to correctly tell the story.
